134efdb643e1375dd92b6c7f5.png\" width=\"1553\" alt=\"alt text\"></noscript></p>\n","cover_image":"/work/images/best.png","company":"NinjaTrader LLC","tags":[{"id":"Technical writing","path":"/tag/Technical%20writing/","title":"Technical writing"}],"subjects":[{"id":".NET/C#","path":"/subject/.NET%2FC%23/","title":".NET/C#"},{"id":"NinjaTrader","path":"/subject/NinjaTrader/","title":"NinjaTrader"},{"id":"DirectX","path":"/subject/DirectX/","title":"DirectX"}]}},{"node":{"title":"Multi-Threading Consideration for NinjaScript - NinjaTrader 8 Help Guide","path":"/content/work/multi-threading-consideration-for-ninja-script-ninj/","date":"June 2016","timeToRead":1,"description":"NinjaScript was event-driven and multi-threaded, which meant that 3rd party C# developers needed to be aware of how to handle programming scenarios that sometimes needed to be dispatched between parallel threads.","content":"\n","cover_image":"/work/images/multi.png","company":"NinjaTrader LLC","tags":[{"id":"Technical writing","path":"/tag/Technical%20writing/","title":"Technical writing"}],"subjects":[{"id":".NET/C#","path":"/subject/.NET%2FC%23/","title":".NET/C#"},{"id":"Multi-threaded programming","path":"/subject/Multi-threaded%20programming/","title":"Multi-threaded programming"},{"id":"NinjaTrader","path":"/subject/NinjaTrader/","title":"NinjaTrader"}]}},{"node":{"title":"NinjaScript Lifecycle - NinjaTrader 8 Help Guide","path":"/content/work/ninja-script-lifecycle-ninja-trader-8-help-guide/","date":"June 2016","timeToRead":1,"description":"NinjaTrader provided a custom classes of programming interfaces that were given low-level access to core software objects to make it easy to develop custom add-ons, yet were wrapped in abstract layers that were sometimes not so easy to understand in common debug scenarios. To help with the learning curve, I worked with the team of product managers and engineers to help ensure that 3rd party developers understood how each instance of their custom NinjaScript types would be expected to be handled by core NinjaTrader platform.","content":"<p><img class=\"g-image g-image--lazy g-image--loading\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg fill='none' viewBox='0 0 1549 1272' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3e%3cdefs%3e%3cfilter id='__svg-blur-fb67490067f7092b446d3fafbd442e1d'%3e%3cfeGaussianBlur in='SourceGraphic' stdDeviation='40'/%3e%3c/filter%3e%3c/defs%3e%3cimage x='0' y='0' filter='url(%23__svg-blur-fb67490067f7092b446d3fafbd442e1d)' width='1549' height='1272' xlink:href='data:image/png%3bbase64%2ciVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAEAAAAA1CAIAAAB%2b5Hr7AAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAPYklEQVRo3s2a%2b48kx13A558ACSNhIQUkyC9WIIlkJGyJ8ANCYKFERMSEc%2bTwK1KQIgEiEUkwIEWCUx5A4vOd8AWTs3258%2b29fWfv3u7t7szO%2b9kz0/Oe6Xl29/T0Y3qey6e7duf27mwfMud1SrW13/rWt6vr%2b6xvVU9AVRRd04zhUFOUXlEeVGt9uaQ2Gpqq2vN58Lv/%2bvqnPnv%2b6Wfe%2bPTTF5/9/XO/Bfy7F5753IVnP3f%2bd54999Sn/%2bvJT7z6q7/%2bk1/7zeOpZz/xG6998qnXP/P0uad%2b%2b9xnnv7OU58NDDV1aAxHxtBQVV1RtGZTbzaH/X6xKGu2FfvPl68%2b9/m3//zEzS/9xfU//dKV575w8/kTF575vbefP3Hji8%2bv/cEf3/yzL8PP6V/85TNPPHnml37lo61PPPnKLzwBA1c//8W1P3zu0h/9yT988lOBrpS3RiPLtm3HscdjqmnbpmUN%2bn1rMsmce%2bPOX31t76V/2f3mt7f/5u93/u4boW/94%2bZff337b78BvPvNb1E3v/b1t0%2b8SL31wlf/L/X2V6h/%2baHrrRdevHXixdsvfPX6l79y8gvPBxqlcqfT6fV6iqK0220A0zQNwxiNRrquW5a1T1ku91dlcQiDPIo/9uK47uWb7wQisVgikZAkKRwO7%2b7uxmKxer3OulGJ4ASWmq1WrVbr9nptvzQprRbswjNAvdHodrvpdLrRaDT9gkSgF5S04IV0Wq1WpVJRVfWxMOC67q31zUAqlcpms7QsYjDAcLzC0mEAJQBABwxL4/HYwcx8eNWCgQxgOBwKetEV9GIS0XX8AsCEvH4%2bn0%2bnU9rZbDb3ywoQQ6JLCzyZTAAWi4VowQsGbq9vBRB/MpmMRqMIHjrXL%2bJNvJsWJSDOcrlcrVYLhUKpVEKu5VKpKBfrzUatXq/5BRkzQyQSYTa6siwjbDA8BcxTVb%2bgBNkvDGUyGbodvwAwyiSeqrtdMSFKYwjrgBIpa5pGl1GGPAYmk9t37gYyfoENlND2rYKCEhAbS6fFE1h3LpeT/MK7mb1YLGYzGaVSKecLWb9AkM/nIWBlgs%2bSLEMGG7R%%2b23dLUD0G3X2q1Kr1MHoIXGGHZpeRxiMZumKpraBkkX2BoNGOVZXW17LdMavfF4aIwGhtHX9M7Q6Buj/lDvTMbD/SV%2b4tzZCXkmhKUKDdiH5ZAByzUJQKlQ8O7W5u290FYssrOzvR4Nb6eSYSkblwupXDaeSUWy6WixkM7nEsVCKh4LJhN7e8GtSHg7GtnlweDOR